    <string name="missionTitle">Know your numbers, grow your shop</string>
    <string name="missionBody1Pre">I&apos;m a </string>
    <string name="missionBody1Highlight">senior software developer</string>
    <string name="missionBody1Post"> who spent 4 years managing AlgoriX, an Etsy shop, alongside my day job. Every month I&apos;d waste time manually piecing together revenue, order counts, and trends just to answer basic questions. SellerScope fixes that.</string>
